name: Central Doge Republic Meme
description: CDR is a fungible crypto asset created on the Solana blockchain, representing the official meme of the Central Doge Republic Meme and supported by DogeCoin itself. CDR Meme is intended to serve as a symbol and support for the ideals represented by the Central Doge Republic Meme. $CDR is not designed to be, nor should it be considered, an investment opportunity, investment contract, or security of any kind.
